{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a883077b88","title":"在留守兵团成立大会上的讲话摘要","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d3a2288f8a","index":0,"year":1937,"month":12,"day":null,"articleId":"a883077b88"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji11","name":"毛泽东全集第11卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji11.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji11":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5aec409b6e","type":"paragraph","text":"在留守兵团成立大会上的讲话摘要“","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"a883077b88"},{"id":"18f1e021b6","type":"paragraph","text":"（1937年12月）军队是根据地赖以存在的必要不可少的武装力量，要把留守任务看得同前线抗日救国一样的重要，要使留守兵团尽快走上正规化的建军道路。[1]1937年12月，八路军留守兵团正式成立，毛泽东在大会上作了重要讲话，这是毛泽东讲话的一部分。这次会议还确定了“加强战斗准备，部队正规化建设，统一战线教育，增强部队纪律，紧密与人民的团结”为兵团这一阶段的主要工作。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"a883077b88"}],"page":{"id":"7a48d2cf9f","publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"a883077b88","start":429,"end":429}}}},"__N_SSG":true}